             sworn.</p>
               <p>This is my pot.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I came from sea last Friday sevennight; I was rather in liquor, and I did not recollect any thing of the transaction; I told Mr. Le Mar that I was going to get a ship, and he said they would get a ship for me, and hoped they should hang me; there was a man that said he knew me, and desired him not to drag me along; he said he knew me in business for myself, and that I bore a good character: I have been a master cooper.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17901208-33-verdict176" type="verdictDescription">
